{"tid":2439993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保險業：接種疫苗現副作用不納入個人意外保險","createTime":"2021-03-09T15:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T08:34:08.000Z","uid":103207,"like":85,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ef2467017a7f258cddba3882e87619b71ea52a","tid":2439993,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"香港蘋果日報<br />\n <br />\n本港上月底開展接種武漢肺炎疫苗計劃，至今發生至少5宗嚴重異常事件，其中3人死亡，2人需接受深切治療，另有多人不適送院。部份個案經專家委員會初步檢視後，認為與接種疫苗沒有直接關係，能否獲政府疫苗保障基金補償仍存疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">有保險業人士指出，若接種疫苗後出現嚴重病況或不幸逝世，不會納入個人意外保險保障，「因為你明知去打針（接種），有個風險喺度，而唔係不可預料之事（unforeseeable）」。<br />\n市民接種疫苗前，須簽署「接種須知」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">市民應知接種風險 意外保險難受理</span><br />\n<br />\n市民接種疫苗前，須簽署「接種須知」，以確認已閱讀及明白接種須知的內容等，包括可能出現的副作用。資深保險業人士潘榮輝指出，除非有附加條款，一般個人意外保險涵蓋的範圍，不包括接種疫苗後出現的副作用或引致身體受傷，因投保人接種疫苗前，理應清楚知道有關風險，「一般意外都唔會保，因為係你明知嘅事，知道有風險嘅事」。<br />\n<br />\n潘榮輝續指，若投保人因接種疫苗後出現身體不適需住院接受治療，一般醫療保險都會提供有關的住院費用保障，金額視乎保單內容而定，但就不會有額外補償。<span class=\"red\">他指出，若投保人接種疫苗後出現嚴重狀況如癱瘓或半身不遂等，部份危疾保險都會有保障，但需要醫生證明有關狀況是因接種疫苗後所致。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/I3KXUHU3HZH45EREGWT2V5IYQQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0GLyBwzLNyeI24hGPLyOHhNdLtlqSLdeF3g9oYTc8OQSlmjVFYl3WmrSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FI3KXUHU3HZH45EREGWT2V5IYQQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0GLyBwzLNyeI24hGPLyOHhNdLtlqSLdeF3g9oYTc8OQSlmjVFYl3WmrSI&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=848bb7d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FI3KXUHU3HZH45EREGWT2V5IYQQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0GLyBwzLNyeI24hGPLyOHhNdLtlqSLdeF3g9oYTc8OQSlmjVFYl3WmrSI&h=d3ee2340\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/I3KXUHU3HZH45EREGWT2V5IYQQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0GLyBwzLNyeI24hGPLyOHhNdLtlqSLdeF3g9oYTc8OQSlmjVFYl3WmrSI</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0742a62ec44f6552d9048ea98d6d2d809d2cd216","tid":2439993,"uid":56819,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"真慘,做完白老鼠,冇咗200萬,仲要claim唔到保險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8675b786795a4e47e351321ee5817d9362426e1c","tid":2439993,"uid":288913,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"0742a62ec44f6552d9048ea98d6d2d809d2cd216","tid":2439993,"uid":56819,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"真慘,做完白老鼠,冇咗200萬,仲要claim唔到保險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"連保險都失效埋，賠了夫人又折兵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9d58160c9ba7f516662dcac8abeb9cb260663f","tid":2439993,"uid":193026,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"8675b786795a4e47e351321ee5817d9362426e1c","tid":2439993,"uid":288913,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"0742a62ec44f6552d9048ea98d6d2d809d2cd216","tid":2439993,"uid":56819,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"真慘,做完白老鼠,冇咗200萬,仲要claim唔到保險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"連保險都失效埋，賠了夫人又折兵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a